## âœ… Step 2: Create `landing.routes.ts`

Inside:
ðŸ“ `client/src/app/features/landing/`

Create a new file:

ðŸ“„ `landing.routes.ts`

### Paste this content:

```ts
import { Routes } from '@angular/router';
import { LandingComponent } from './landing.component';

export const LANDING_ROUTES: Routes = [
  {
    path: '',
    component: LandingComponent,
  },
];
```

---

## âœ… Step 3: Connect `landing.routes.ts` to `app.routes.ts`

Open this file:
ðŸ“„ `client/src/app/app.routes.ts`

Update it like this:

```ts
import { Routes } from '@angular/router';

export const routes: Routes = [
  {
    path: '',
    loadChildren: () =>
      import('./features/landing/landing.routes').then(m => m.LANDING_ROUTES),
  }
];
```

